  "2389220": {
    "name": "Sandara: City of a Thousand Eclipses",
    "steam_appid": 2389220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/1c79b53737b07050099a6af7c2a8fdd4.webp?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沙朵拉是一款角色扮演剧情向卡牌游戏. 它设定在一片荒芜沙漠, 玩家透过管理牌组生存下去. 你长大了. 可以离开孩儿岛, 可以了解长者智语, 可以成为优良公民, 可以搬到独石. 你的长老会教导你如何讨生活. 努力工作, 达到配额, 避免麻烦. 城市掌握着你的一举一动, 聆听着你的一言一语. 稍有不慎你将被这城市吞没. 沙朵拉: 千日蚀城是一款角色扮演剧情向卡牌游戏. 它座落在一块叫做&quot;独石&quot; 的神秘岩石上, 屹立在一片寸草不生, 广袤无垠的沙漠&quot;匝门&quot;之中. 平日里的独石作为沙朵拉:千日蚀城的地基, 一直沉睡着, 和普通的山峦并无二致. 但是每逢日蚀之时, 饥饿的沙漠唤醒这块灰石, 把它变成一颗闪烁着血色的红宝石, 独石将会吞没一切无用之人.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/635b2f61aa23c04af92665042da69ba1.webp?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/24572ce540a7f81886e82dc45e312f7e.poster.avif?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/24572ce540a7f81886e82dc45e312f7e.webm?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/24572ce540a7f81886e82dc45e312f7e.mp4?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沙朵拉: 千日蚀城会提供玩家一个丰富的故事. 玩家可以依据自己的喜好打造卡牌, 获取经验, 金钱, 以及物资. 开拓新地区和完成任务合成新的卡牌, 强化牌组.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/e190381044bd5fd66fd101af0ed23d80.webp?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/78a9194a2529653d655353bdbfc36ad4.poster.avif?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/78a9194a2529653d655353bdbfc36ad4.webm?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/78a9194a2529653d655353bdbfc36ad4.mp4?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沙朵拉分成三个地区, 硗地, 中枢, 乐土, 各有各的特色. 一区享受荣华富贵, 另一区生灵涂炭. 你会选择站哪边? 走哪条道? 你选择的同伴决定你的命运.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/cd9b66ae8bcefadddeccf7175100297b.webp?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/b40d4e0c765530e15cee51e34f30c7e1.poster.avif?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/b40d4e0c765530e15cee51e34f30c7e1.webm?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/b40d4e0c765530e15cee51e34f30c7e1.mp4?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探险更远的地方, 带领沙朵拉的人民脱离下沉中的独石. 揭开古老的秘密, 发现遗忘的地区.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/0793e4277b8e9d6f6cc00de340af4771.webp?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/c40607163fc1c5f767f9ed45a7619969.poster.avif?t=1731314842\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/c40607163fc1c5f767f9ed45a7619969.webm?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389220/extras/c40607163fc1c5f767f9ed45a7619969.mp4?t=1731314842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你很快就会发现你的天赋: 孩子的语言- 幼语, 即便学了长者智语之后也不会忘掉. 探索独石的秘密, 已故孩童的灵魂仍在游荡于城市中.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
